  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Leo goes to a packing store to buy containers and tape. Leo has <math alttext=\"dollar sign 15\"><mo>$</mo><mn>15</mn></math>. Each container costs\u00a0<math alttext=\"dollar sign 1.87\"><mo>$</mo><mn>1.87</mn></math> and each roll of tape costs <math alttext=\"dollar sign 2.40\"><mo>$</mo><mn>2.40</mn></math>. Which inequality represents the relationship between the number of containers, <math alttext=\"c\"><mi>c</mi>\n</math>, and the number of rolls of tape, <math alttext=\"t\"><mi>t</mi>\n</math>, Leo can buy?</p>",
